---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
  <!-- HERO with upfront CTA via Beehiiv + promo -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1 class="brand">Modern Compass</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Helping you find direction in the moments that matter most.
      </p>
      <p class="sublead">
        Modern Compass is a framework for growth in Self, Trust, Character, and Relationships.
      </p>

      <!-- Promo + Beehiiv embed as a single unit -->
      <div class="newsletter-embed">
        <img
          src="/Newsletter%20Promo.png"
          alt="Join 100+ subscribers and get this digital asset free"
          class="promo"
        />
        <script async src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/embed.js"></script>
        <iframe
          src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/261a3276-40ab-431a-8523-c85bec095b96"
          class="beehiiv-embed"
          data-test-id="beehiiv-embed"
          frameborder="0"
          scrolling="no"
          style="width:100%; height:439px; margin:0; border-radius:0; background-color:transparent; box-shadow:none; max-width:100%; display:block;"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT MODERN COMPASS IS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">What Modern Compass is</h2>
      <p>
        Most personal growth advice is either vague inspiration or rigid systems. Modern Compass is different.
        It is built around four clear directions that are simple to remember and deep enough to guide real decisions.
      </p>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Self</h3>
          <p>Understand your worth and confidence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Trust</h3>
          <p>Sharpen how you place it and how you earn it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Character</h3>
          <p>Align who you are with what you do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Relationships</h3>
          <p>Grow deeper and healthier connections.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY IT MATTERS -->
  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">Why it matters</h2>
      <p>
        Life does not come with a map. Every choice pulls you somewhere. Without clarity, you drift.
        With Modern Compass, you have a tool to orient yourself, test your decisions, and move with confidence.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROOF AND MOMENTUM -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">Proof and momentum</h2>
      <p>
        Over one hundred people use tools like the TimeOS Audit, the Impulse Wallet, and the Intention vs Action Activity
        to reclaim time, take action, and grow with intention.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECOND INVITE -->
  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2 class="h">Get TimeOS free and join the newsletter</h2>
      <p class="narrow">
        I share one monthly email with no fluff, only practical tools and insights you can use right away.
        As a welcome you will get the TimeOS Audit free in your first email, a five dollar value.
      </p>

      <!-- Reuse the same embed for a bottom CTA if you want it in two places.
           If you prefer a single embed, you can remove this block. -->
      <div class="newsletter-embed">
        <script async src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/embed.js"></script>
        <iframe
          src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/261a3276-40ab-431a-8523-c85bec095b96"
          class="beehiiv-embed"
          data-test-id="beehiiv-embed"
          frameborder="0"
          scrolling="no"
          style="width:100%; height:439px; margin:0; border-radius:0; background-color:transparent; box-shadow:none; max-width:700px; display:block;"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSING NOTE -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">A personal note</h2>
      <p>
        I created Modern Compass because I got tired of watching personal growth stay stuck in clich√©s.
        If you are ready for clarity, tools that actually work, and a framework you can use in real life, welcome.
        Always follow your compass.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Layout helpers */
  .wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .wrap.narrow { max-width: 800px; }
  .section { padding: 56px 0; background: #ffffff; color: #111; }
  .section.alt { background: #f8fafc; }

  /* Hero */
  .hero { padding: 56px 0 28px; text-align: center; background: #ffffff; color: #111; }
  .brand {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #b324a7, #0087c9, #f5c242, #f76a3e);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text; color: transparent;
  }
  .lead { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 6px 0; color: #222; }
  .sublead { font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #444; }

  /* Promo + Beehiiv as a single unit */
  .newsletter-embed {
    display: grid;
    justify-items: center;
    row-gap: 8px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 700px;
  }
  .promo {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px; /* controls promo size so it is not huge */
    height: auto;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .newsletter-embed > * { margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; line-height: 0; }
  .beehiiv-embed { display: block; margin-top: -12px !important; }

  /* Content blocks */
  .h { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #111; }
  .h3 { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 4px 0; color: #111; }
  p { margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #333; }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .beehiiv-embed { margin-top: -8px !important; }
  }
</style>
